Evolution Markets executive briefingAttached please find the most recent edition of Evolution Markets executive briefing on key issues impacting the energy and environmental markets In this edition Early Crediting for JI Projects Is a Useful Policy Instrument Analysis by John Palmisano Managing Director of Evolution Markets LLC click on below link to access the briefing assetsevobriefsnwpdf We send these briefings by email every few weeks or more frequently if fresh breaking news merits a special edition Our goal is to offer the timeliest and most insightful analysis on news developments that directly impact the markets we serve We would greatly appreciate your feedback on how to improve this publication and on suggested future topics We will also invite prominent industry figures to contribute to surveys and interviews on relevant topics and look forward to your participation Please direct comments regarding the content of our Brief and suggestions for future issues to my attention Sincerely John Palmisano Managing Director Evolution Markets LLC If you would like to be removed from our distribution list please change your preferences following this link scriptsbackdoorphpuserexpandacabfbafcallermodacc Note that sharing or forwarding this message and the active links to restricted sections of the Evolution Markets website is the same as sharing your password and is a violation of the Evolution Markets LLC Restricted Website Access User Agreement If you would like to refer our website to your friend or associate use the below link referphp For technical problems related to accessing our resources please contact our webmaster For general feedback on improving our site we would appreciate your input feedbackhtml
